        "questionText":"What are the main uses of this keyword?",
        "answer":"<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>There are the following uses of&nbsp;<strong>this<\/strong>&nbsp;keyword.<\/p>\r\n<ul class=\"points\">\r\n<li><strong>this<\/strong>&nbsp;can be used to refer to the current class instance variable.<\/li>\r\n<li><strong>this<\/strong>&nbsp;can be used to invoke current class method (implicitly)<\/li>\r\n<li><strong>this()<\/strong>&nbsp;can be used to invoke the current class constructor.<\/li>\r\n<li><strong>this<\/strong>&nbsp;can be passed as an argument in the method call.<\/li>\r\n<li><strong>this<\/strong>&nbsp;can be passed as an argument in the constructor call.<\/li>\r\n<li><strong>this<\/strong>&nbsp;can be used to return the current class instance from the method.<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>"
