        "answer":"<ul>\r\n<li>\r\n<p>As we know, that this refers to the current class object, therefore, it must be similar to the current class object. However, there can be two main advantages of passing this into a method instead of the current class object.<\/p>\r\n<ul class=\"points\">\r\n<li>this is a final variable. Therefore, this cannot be assigned to any new value whereas the current class object might not be final and can be changed.<\/li>\r\n<li>this can be used in the synchronized block.<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>"
